comments: Noel (NYK) places his arm against Towns (MIN) and the contact is marginal.  Towns then clamps Noel's arm into his own body.
Rubio (MIN) and Gibson (NYK) engage in marginal arm to arm contact during the off-ball screen.
Towns (MIN) briefly places a hand on Barrett's (NYK) back prior to making contact with the ball during Barrett's driving shot attempt. Towns immediately removes his hand and the contact is marginal.
Gibson (NYK) and Towns (MIN) briefly engage in marginal arm to arm contact prior to disengaging.
Rose (NYK) legally contests Rubio's (MIN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Towns (MIN) makes contact to Randle's (NYK) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Rubio (MIN) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
Burks (NYK) moves into Rubio's (MIN) body and the contact affects his shot attempt.
Rubio (MIN) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) arm after he secures the rebound.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Burks (NYK).
